(40, 16, 23, 50, 3, 19, 19, 'savourest not the things that be of God', 'Focus on Earthly vs. Divine', 'This connection highlights the contrast between valuing earthly things and divine priorities. Both passages emphasize the danger of prioritizing human desires over God''s will.', 'theme', 0.45399999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
