(40, 16, 23, 46, 2, 14, 15, 'savourest not the things that be of God', 'Spiritual Discernment and Human Understanding', 'This connection highlights the contrast between spiritual and natural understanding. Both passages emphasize that the things of God are not comprehended by those who prioritize human perspectives.', 'theme', 0.40499999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
